<style>
    body {
      -ms-overflow-style: scrollbar;
      overflow-y: scroll;
      overscroll-behavior-y: none;
    }

    .errorContainer {
      background-color: #FFF;
      color: #0F1419;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 10%;
      font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .errorButton {
      margin: 3em 0;
    }

    .errorButton a {
      background: #1DA1F2;
      border-radius: 2.5em;
      color: white;
      padding: 1em 2em;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .errorButton a:hover,
    .errorButton a:focus {
      background: rgb(26, 145, 218);
    }

    .errorFooter {
      color: #657786;
      font-size: 80%;
      line-height: 1.5;
      padding: 1em 0;
    }

    .errorFooter a,
    .errorFooter a:visited {
      color: #657786;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding-right: 1em;
    }

    .errorFooter a:hover,
    .errorFooter a:active {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
